# Python Time Module Practice

This repository contains beginner Python programs using the `time` module and basic command-line concepts.

## Topics Covered
- Current time functions
- Time delay using sleep()
- Time shifting examples
- Command-line utility basics

## Files
- current_time_example.py
- time_sleep_example.py
- time_shift_example.py
- command_line_utility.py

## Learning Goal
To understand Python's time-related functions and basic CLI programming concepts.
